- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is relevant as the paper discusses the design and evaluation of a full-fledged system. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper aims to allocate resources efficiently and improve system performance. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with high-level compositions of frameworks and their components.
